crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis: This is a Go-based proxy malware. It leverages the 'github.com/armon/go-socks5' and 'github.com/hashicorp/yamux' libraries to implement a SOCKS5 proxy server. This functionality allows a remote attacker to use the infected machine as a proxy to tunnel network traffic, a common backdoor technique. The presence and use of these specific libraries are strong indicators of its malicious purpose.
